txt.en: Your efforts in An Shêru has earned you the status of friend among the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh.
Your continued efforts to support An Shêru earns you greater favour with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh.
Friend of the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh
You must earn Friend standing with the Temámir of Jiret-menêsh
